ais" lang="ja" hreflang="ja" class="interlanguage-link-target">日本語</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-jv"><a href="https://jv.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dalai_Lama_ping_14" title="Dalai Lama ping 14 — javanais" lang="jv" hreflang="jv" class="interlanguage-link-target">Jawa</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ka"><a href="https://ka.wikipedia.org/wiki/XIV_%E1%83%93%E1%83%90%E1%83%9A%E1%83%90%E1%83%98_%E1%83%9A%E1%83%90%E1%83%9B%E1%83%90" title="XIV დალაი ლამა — géorgien" lang="ka" hreflang="ka" class="interlanguage-link-target">ქართული</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-kab"><a href="https://kab.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adalaylama_wis_14" title="Adalaylama wis 14 — kabyle" lang="kab" hreflang="kab" class="interlanguage-link-target">Taqbaylit</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-km"><a href="https://km.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E1%9E%9F%E1%9E%98%E1%9F%92%E1%9E%8F%E1%9F%81%E1%9E%85_Dalai_Lama_%E1%9E%91%E1%9E%B8_14" title="សម្តេច Dalai Lama ទី 14 — khmer" lang="km" hreflang="km" class="interlanguage-link-target">ភាសាខ្មែរ</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-kn"><a href="https://kn.wikipedia.org/wiki/14_%E0%B2%A8%E0%B3%87_%E0%B2%A6%E0%B2%B2%E0%B3%88_%E0%B2%B2%E0%B2%BE%E0%B2%AE%E0%B2%BE" title="14 ನೇ ದಲೈ ಲಾಮಾ — kannada" lang="kn" hreflang="kn" class="interlanguage-link-target">ಕನ್ನಡ</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ko"><a href="https://ko.wikipedia.org/wiki/%EC%A0%9C14%EB%8C%80_%EB%8B%AC%EB%9D%BC%EC%9D%B4_%EB%9D%BC%EB%A7%88" title="제14대 달라이 라마 — coréen" lang="ko" hreflang="ko" class="interlanguage-link-target">한국어</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ksh"><a href="https://ksh.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tenzin_Gyatso" title="Tenzin Gyatso — kölsch" lang="ksh" hreflang="ksh" class="interlanguage-link-target">Ripoarisch</a></li><li class="interlanguage-link interwiki-ky"><a href="https://ky.wikipedia.org/wiki/%D0%94%D0%B0%D0%BB%D0%B0%D0%B9-%D0%BB%D0%B0%D0%BC%D0%B0_XIV" title="Далай-лама XIV — kirghize" lang="ky" href