<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-9"><a href="#Séjour_à_Yatoung"><span class="tocnumber">1.3</span> <span class="toctext">Séjour à Yatoung</span></a></li>
<li class="toclevel-2 tocsection-10"><a href="#Coexistence_dans_le_cadre_de_l&#39;accord_en_17_points"><span class="tocnumber">1.4</span> <span class="toctext">Coexistence dans le cadre de l'accord en 17 points</span></a></li>
