<li id="cite_note-89"><span class="mw-cite-backlink noprint"><a href="#cite_ref-89">↑</a> </span><span class="reference-text">Michael Harris Goodman, <abbr class="abbr nowrap italique" title="opere citato (« dans l&#39;ouvrage cité »)">op. cit.</abbr>, <span class="nowrap"><abbr class="abbr" title="page(s)">p.</abbr>&#160;183-184</span>.</span>
