<li id="cite_note-Ngabo_Ngawang_Jigme-101"><span class="mw-cite-backlink noprint">↑ <sup><a href="#cite_ref-Ngabo_Ngawang_Jigme_101-0">a</a> et <a href="#cite_ref-Ngabo_Ngawang_Jigme_101-1">b</a></sup> </span><span class="reference-text"><abbr class="abbr indicateur-langue" title="Langue : anglais">(en)</abbr> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2005-08/30/content_3422747.htm">Ngapoi recalls the founding of the TAR</a>, <i>China View</i>, 30 août 2005.</span>
