<li id="cite_note-154"><span class="mw-cite-backlink noprint"><a href="#cite_ref-154">↑</a> </span><span class="reference-text"><abbr class="abbr indicateur-langue" title="Langue : anglais">(en)</abbr> <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.claudearpi.net/maintenance/uploaded_pics/Mao_Khrushchev_1959.pdf">Memorandum of Conversation of. N.S. Khrushchev with Mao Zedong, Beijing, 2 October 1959</a>.</span>
