<li id="cite_note-163"><span class="mw-cite-backlink noprint"><a href="#cite_ref-163">↑</a> </span><span class="reference-text"><abbr class="abbr indicateur-langue" title="Langue : anglais">(en)</abbr> Arjun Sawhney, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://www.galleryespace.com/about_spot_in_the_mountain.php">A Spot in the Mountains</a>.</span>
